IPO PRICING - Peerless prices at $ 11 / shr . Company Name Peerless Systems Inc Priced At $ 11 . 00 Number of Shares 3 , 750 , 000 Lead Underwriter Hambrecht & Quist LLCNote : The company said that 2 , 500 , 000 shares are being sold by the company , 1 , 073 , 978 shares are being sold by the selling securityholders and 176 , 022 shares are being sold by the underwriters . Note : The company and the Selling Securityholders also granted the underwriters an option to purchase up to an aggregate of 562 , 500 additional shares of its common stock to cover over - allotments . Peerless intends to use the net proceeds from the sale for the repayment of indebtedness and equipment lease lines , working capital and general corporate purposes , it said . - - New York Newsdesk 212 - 859 - 1610 
